properties.Name: MineralType
properties.Description:
A mineral is a naturally occurring chemical compound.

Ex:
- Antlerite 
- Atacamite
- Azurite
- Bornite (Peacock Ore) 
- Chalcocite 
- Chalcopyrite 
- Chrysocolla 
- Copper Carbonate
- Covellite 
- Cuprite 
- Digenite
- Malachite
- Phosphate
- Sulfate
